name: CUSTOM case
description:
PLEASE READ BEFORE PURCHASING!

Purchase this item if:

1. You would like one of our existing designs (dripping CC or LV etc.) on a GALAXY case.

2. You would like an iPhone or Galaxy case personalized with your name.

DO NOT purchase this item if:

1. You want a Fine Ass Girls case. (Coming Soon)

2. You want a case personalized with your logo. 
(If you are looking to personalize cases with your logo I offer this option for wholesale. Email me with a picture for prices).

If you have a phone other than Galaxy or iPhone please CONTACT ME FIRST to ensure that your case is available.

Once you have purchased this item, contact me with the subject being your first and last name and the body containing the model of your phone, the color of case you would like, as well as the color you would like your name to be in (default will be gold). 

THESE ARE MADE TO ORDER. Please allow up 3-4 weeks for shipping!

The photos include a font example.
